      <title>菲律宾比索跌破 57 美元兑关键水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/philippine-peso-weakens-past-key-57-per-dollar-level-lv345342</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储将推迟降息的预期打压风险资产，菲律宾比索自 2022 年底以来首次跌破备受关注的 57 兑美元水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/philippine-peso-weakens-past-key-57-per-dollar-level-lv345342</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 01:07:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
